## ðŸš€ åŠŸèƒ½ç‰¹ç‚¹

- æ‰¹é‡å¼‚æ­¥å‘é€ HTTP è¯·æ±‚ï¼ˆæ”¯æŒ GET / POSTï¼‰
- æ”¯æŒè‡ªå®šä¹‰ headers / params / timeout / tag
- æ”¯æŒå…¨å±€è¶…æ—¶æ—¶é—´æŽ§åˆ¶ï¼ˆ`total_timeout`ï¼‰
- è¿”å›žå“åº”å†…å®¹ã€é”™è¯¯ä¿¡æ¯ã€Meta æ•°æ®
- ä½¿ç”¨ Rust + Tokio æå‡åžåèƒ½åŠ›

## ðŸ“¦ ä½¿ç”¨ç¤ºä¾‹

```python
import asyncio
import time
import rusty_req


async def main():
    # ä½¿ç”¨ JSONPlaceholder - ä¸€ä¸ªå…è´¹æµ‹è¯• API
    requests = [
        rusty_req.RequestItem(
            url="https://httpbin.org/delay/2",
            method="GET",
            headers={
                "Accept-Encoding": "gzip, deflate, br",
                "Connection": "keep-alive",
                "X-Test-Header": "ChatGPT"
            },
            timeout=2.9,
            tag=f"json-test-{i}",
        )
        for i in range(100)  # 100 ä¸ªå¹¶å‘è¯·æ±‚
    ]

    # å…³é—­è°ƒè¯•è¾“å‡º
    rusty_req.set_debug(False)

    print("ðŸš€ å¼€å§‹ 100 ä¸ªå¹¶å‘ JSON API è¯·æ±‚...")
    start_time = time.perf_counter()

    responses = await rusty_req.fetch_requests(
        requests,
        total_timeout=3.0
    )

    total_time = time.perf_counter() - start_time

    # å¤„ç†ç»“æžœ
    success = 0
    failed = 0
    status_codes = {}
    response_times = []

    for r in responses:
        if r.get("exception"):
            failed += 1
        else:
            meta = r.get('meta', {})
            status_code = meta.get("status_code", 0)
            process_time = float(meta.get("process_time", 0))

            status_codes[status_code] = status_codes.get(status_code, 0) + 1
            response_times.append(process_time)
            success += 1

    # è®¡ç®—ç»Ÿè®¡æ•°æ®
    avg_response_time = sum(response_times) / len(response_times) if response_times else 0
    min_response_time = min(response_times) if response_times else 0
    max_response_time = max(response_times) if response_times else 0
    req_per_sec = success / total_time if total_time > 0 else 0

    print("\nðŸ“Š è´Ÿè½½æµ‹è¯•ç»“æžœ:")
    print(f"â±ï¸ æ€»è€—æ—¶: {total_time:.2f}s")
    print(f"ðŸ“ˆ è¯·æ±‚æ¯ç§’: {req_per_sec:.1f}")
    print(f"âœ… æˆåŠŸè¯·æ±‚æ•°: {success}")
    print(f"âš ï¸ å¤±è´¥è¯·æ±‚æ•°: {failed}")
    print(f"ðŸ”„ çŠ¶æ€ç åˆ†å¸ƒ: {status_codes}")
    print(f"â³ å“åº”æ—¶é—´ - å¹³å‡: {avg_response_time:.4f}s, æœ€å°: {min_response_time:.4f}s, æœ€å¤§: {max_response_time:.4f}s")


if __name__ == "__main__":
    asyncio.run(main())
```

## ðŸ§± æ•°æ®ç»“æž„è¯´æ˜Ž

### `RequestItem` å‚æ•°

| å­—æ®µå     | ç±»åž‹             | å¿…é¡» | è¯´æ˜Ž                                   |
|------------|------------------|------|----------------------------------------|
| `url`      | `str`            | âœ…   | è¯·æ±‚åœ°å€                               |
| `method`   | `str`            | âœ…   | è¯·æ±‚æ–¹æ³•ï¼ˆ`"GET"` æˆ– `"POST"`ï¼‰        |
| `params`   | `dict` / `None`  | å¦   | æŸ¥è¯¢å‚æ•°ï¼ˆGETï¼‰æˆ–è¡¨å•æ•°æ®ï¼ˆPOSTï¼‰      |
| `headers`  | `dict` / `None`  | å¦   | è‡ªå®šä¹‰è¯·æ±‚å¤´                           |
| `timeout`  | `float`          | âœ…   | å•ä¸ªè¯·æ±‚è¶…æ—¶ï¼ˆç§’ï¼‰                     |
| `tag`      | `str`            | å¦   | æ ‡è®°è¯·æ±‚çš„æ¥æºã€ç¼–å·ç­‰è¾…åŠ©ä¿¡æ¯         |

